 <PERSON> Alison </PERSON> <PERSON> Smale </PERSON>, The <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> bureau chief in <LOCATION> Vienna </LOCATION>, regularly covers <LOCATION> Yugoslavia </LOCATION> and traveled to <LOCATION> Belgrade </LOCATION> for this story.
